long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
THIS IS THE CANARY DISTRIBUTION OF THE COMPASS EXTENSION, INTENDED FOR DEVELOPERS.

Compass Canary is a distribution channel of the Compass extension for developers that gives them access to additional unstable APIs. The goal is to maximize developer control, so that we can learn the full extent of what developers want to do with Compass, and later incorporate those lessons into the main Compass distribution.

You can find the main / production version of Compass here: https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/compass-wallet-for-sei/anokgmphncpekkhclmingpimjmcooifb
